1
00:00:00,021 --> 00:00:03,381
CBFC

2
00:00:38,101 --> 00:00:41,461
There is another world too
other than ours.

3
00:00:41,741 --> 00:00:43,661
Genies live in there.

4
00:00:44,021 --> 00:00:47,541
Innumerable miracles
happen in their lives.

5
00:00:47,821 --> 00:00:50,581
And their king is Karkimuki.

6
00:00:51,381 --> 00:00:54,341
All the genies in his kingdom
were happy.

7
00:00:54,781 --> 00:00:56,621
But he was very sad.

8
00:00:57,141 --> 00:00:59,741
One thing troubled him a lot.

9
00:01:00,061 --> 00:01:02,741
There is no successor to him.

10
00:01:03,061 --> 00:01:06,221
Public wanted the king
to have a successor.

11
00:01:06,621 --> 00:01:08,901
One who would take over
the kingdom after him.

12
00:01:09,101 --> 00:01:10,741
Public offered prayers.

13
00:01:10,941 --> 00:01:13,981
And a beautiful son was born to him.

14
00:01:15,461 --> 00:01:17,701
King's happiness knew no bounds.

15
00:01:18,061 --> 00:01:20,021
He got his successor.

16
00:01:20,581 --> 00:01:25,021
King raised his son Chinchiniya by
providing him everything.

17
00:01:25,341 --> 00:01:30,021
He showered his entire love
and happiness unto his son.

18
00:01:30,261 --> 00:01:32,621
His son became his world.

19
00:01:33,261 --> 00:01:35,341
When Chinchiniya turned 10,

20
00:01:35,501 --> 00:01:38,141
he expressed a wish to his father.

21
00:01:38,541 --> 00:01:41,061
That he wanted to go to a world,

22
00:01:41,221 --> 00:01:44,301
where sages perform austerities.

23
00:01:44,501 --> 00:01:47,621
Karkimuki didn't ignore his wish,

24
00:01:47,901 --> 00:01:49,661
and took him to that world.

25
00:01:49,901 --> 00:01:54,340
Chinchiniya became mad with
happiness after entering that world.

26
00:01:54,341 --> 00:01:57,060
He was playing hide-and-seek
with his father.

27
00:01:57,061 --> 00:02:00,301
While playing Chinchiniya went
and hid in such a place,

28
00:02:00,461 --> 00:02:04,461
where a sage was offering penance
for thousands of years.

29
00:02:04,621 --> 00:02:07,381
His penance was interrupted
due to Chinchiniya.

30
00:02:11,781 --> 00:02:14,301
Sage became furious in anger.

31
00:02:14,421 --> 00:02:16,781
and started curing Chinchiniya.

32
00:02:17,141 --> 00:02:21,141
Karkimuki started pleading
with the sage,

33
00:02:21,341 --> 00:02:25,421
and begged with him
to forgive Chinchiniya.

34
00:02:25,541 --> 00:02:29,540
But the sage was
not willing to forgive Chinchiniya.

35
00:02:29,541 --> 00:02:35,181
Because Chinchiniya has broken
the penance of thousands of years.

36
00:02:35,461 --> 00:02:37,781
Karkimuki begged in front
of the sage,

37
00:02:37,941 --> 00:02:41,301
to punish him instead of his son.

38
00:02:41,421 --> 00:02:43,461
Karkimuki turned him into a statue,

39
00:02:43,581 --> 00:02:46,900
instead of his son by cursing him.

40
00:02:46,901 --> 00:02:48,261
Sage said,

41
00:02:48,381 --> 00:02:51,141
48 days after settling
himself free,

42
00:02:51,381 --> 00:02:53,460
from the statue, he will
go back to his world.

43
00:02:53,461 --> 00:02:56,980
Only the human who frees you,

44
00:02:56,981 --> 00:02:59,340
from the statue recites the
mantra written on the statue.

45
00:02:59,341 --> 00:03:03,940
Otherwise you'll turn into ashes
in the air forever.

46
00:03:03,941 --> 00:03:06,581
Father and son started crying
after hearing it.

47
00:03:06,741 --> 00:03:10,301
The sage threw him on earth
after turning him into a statue.

48
00:03:34,341 --> 00:03:36,821
"It's a no moon day
and the moon is missing"

49
00:03:36,941 --> 00:03:39,420
"tire India is crazy
for the leader"

50
00:03:39,421 --> 00:03:41,140
"Nagini..."

51
00:03:41,141 --> 00:03:42,061
Thiru!

52
