Go!

152
00:10:15,741 --> 00:10:18,221
DREAM

153
00:10:18,381 --> 00:10:22,140
Why does this word refers
to APJ Abdul Kamal sir?

154
00:10:22,141 --> 00:10:24,701
Because he said
something about dream.

155
00:10:25,101 --> 00:10:26,501
