156
00:10:26,621 --> 00:10:28,940
It is 4 pm by the time
we reach home from school.

157
00:10:28,941 --> 00:10:30,700
And then English tuition at 4 pm.

158
00:10:30,701 --> 00:10:32,061
Maths tuition at 6 pm.

159
00:10:32,181 --> 00:10:33,701
7 pm to 8 pm science tuition.

160
