Silence! Silence!

164
00:10:45,141 --> 00:10:46,061
Listen,

165
00:10:46,701 --> 00:10:49,140
we're not taking about the dreams
we get in sleep.

166
00:10:49,141 --> 00:10:51,941
Dreams are those which
don't let us to sleep, sit down.

167
00:10:52,341 --> 00:10:54,141
