185
00:11:35,461 --> 00:11:38,500
My mummy, father and
all neighbours do the same.

186
00:11:38,501 --> 00:11:40,501
Because I stay in government colony.

187
00:11:44,501 --> 00:11:45,381
Silence!

188
00:11:45,701 --> 00:11:48,140
Listen, bring your father
to school tomorrow. Sit.

189
00:11:48,141 --> 00:11:50,541
