- Super!

203
00:12:24,061 --> 00:12:24,821
Good!

204
00:12:24,981 --> 00:12:25,901
Madam!

205
00:12:26,261 --> 00:12:27,620
Excellent!
- I can, madam.

206
00:12:27,621 --> 00:12:29,020
Very good!
- I can, madam!

207
00:12:29,021 --> 00:12:29,941
Super!

208
