Whenever I say something...

267
00:15:42,941 --> 00:15:45,341
everyone makes fun of me.

268
00:15:47,341 --> 00:15:49,581
Mother, why do I stammer?

269
00:15:58,901 --> 00:16:00,621
You'll become fine soon, Thiru.

270
00:16:01,381 --> 00:16:04,541
My loving son will speak fast.

271
00:16:05,981 --> 00:16:08,541
Calm down, good boys
don't cry like this.

272
00:16:09,141 --> 00:16:10,701
Come to me, calm down.

273
00:16:24,141 --> 00:16:25,261
Open your mouth, child.

274
00:16:26,621 --> 00:16:27,661
Open more.

275
00:16:28,861 --> 00:16:29,741
More.

276
00:16:31,541 --> 00:16:32,381
Lift your head.

277
00:16:33,821 --> 00:16:34,741
Is it paining here?

278
00:16:35,101 --> 00:16:36,661
Here?
Open your mouth again.

279
00:16:39,861 --> 00:16:40,861
Say one, two, three.

280
00:16:41,381 --> 00:16:43,461
One, two, three,

281
00:16:43,741 --> 00:16:45,581
four, five...

282
00:16:46,581 --> 00:16:48,381
si...

283
00:16:49,221 --> 00:16:50,741
Six.
- Six.

284
00:16:51,181 --> 00:16:53,301
Se... sev...
- Okay, relax.

285
00:16:54,741 --> 00:16:56,220
His jaw muscles are flexible now.

286
00:16:56,221 --> 00:16:57,381
Nothing to fear.

287
00:16:57,501 --> 00:16:59,300
Doctor, Thiru will
become fine, isn't it?

288
00:16:59,301 --> 00:17:00,821
He'll become fine very soon.

289
00:17:01,341 --> 00:17:03,220
I'll tell some exercises,
make him do them.

290
00:17:03,221 --> 00:17:06,221
We'll start the next treat
after the improvement, okay.

291
00:17:06,941 --> 00:17:07,981
Thank you, doctor.

292
00:17:09,141 --> 00:17:10,181
'Silent please'

293
00:17:13,701 --> 00:17:14,780
Coming for picnic?

294
00:17:14,781 --> 00:17:16,981
I... don't like.

295
00:17:17,181 --> 00:17:18,821
Come, I'm too going.

296
00:17:19,181 --> 00:17:20,421
You go...
I'm not coming.

297
00:17:23,061 --> 00:17:24,061
Silly boy!

298
00:17:45,501 --> 00:17:47,901
You don't like anyone.
Why are you searching me?

299
00:18:00,261 --> 00:18:01,781
Come, children!
Come!

300
00:18:05,021 --> 00:18:07,381
Make it fast, come fast.
- Wait! Wait! Stand here.

301
00:18:07,501 --> 00:18:08,260
Make a line.

302
00:18:08,261 --> 00:18:09,500
Come in line!

303
00:18:09,501 --> 00:18:11,981
Come here! -Siddharth,
you come and stand here.

304
00:18:12,381 --> 00:18:15,221
Children! Boys and girls
on different sides.

305
00:18:15,421 --> 00:18:18,061
Stand together and
don't leave each others' hand.

306
00:18:18,221 --> 00:18:19,781
Tanya, come this side.

307
00:18:19,941 --> 00:18:21,341
Raju, come to the left.

308
00:18:22,781 --> 00:18:24,460
Is everyone wearing ID card?

309
00:18:24,461 --> 00:18:26,420
Yes, madam!

310
00:18:26,421 --> 00:18:27,220
Very good!

311
00:18:27,221 --> 00:18:29,261
We all will go together in group.

312
00:18:29,381 --> 00:18:31,940
Nobody should go alone,
and don't touch anything.

313
00:18:31,941 --> 00:18:34,660
Take permission from us
if you want to go anywhere. Okay?

314
00:18:34,661 --> 00:18:36,581
Okay, madam!

315
00:18:39,061 --> 00:18:40,701
Madam...
- What Thiru?

316
00:18:42,021 --> 00:18:42,741
Cannot control.

317
00:18:42,861 --> 00:18:44,300
Came just now
and you want to go immediately.

318
00:18:44,301 --> 00:18:45,701
Okay, go and do it fast.

319
00:18:45,861 --> 00:18:46,741
Go.

320
00:19:22,061 --> 00:19:23,061
Mummy!

321
00:19:32,301 --> 00:19:34,260
Help! Help!

322
00:19:34,261 --> 00:19:35,301
Help!

323
00:19:35,581 --> 00:19:37,341
Someone help me!

324
00:19:37,501 --> 00:19:38,621
Someone help me!

325
00:19:54,741 --> 00:19:58,101
Help! Help!

326
00:22:59,981 --> 00:23:06,221
[Chant]

327
00:23:07,101 --> 00:23:08,621
Devil! Devil!

328
00:23:13,421 --> 00:23:14,261
I can see!

329
00:23:14,661 --> 00:23:15,501
I can speak!

330
00:23:15,661 --> 00:23:16,701
I can hear too!

331
00:23:16,941 --> 00:23:17,821
I'm free?

332
00:23:18,021 --> 00:23:19,101
I'm free!

333
00:23:19,261 --> 00:23:20,661
I'm free!

334
00:23:21,461 --> 00:23:24,141
"I'm free! I'm free!"

335
00:23:25,421 --> 00:23:27,141
Where is the one freed me?

336
00:23:27,621 --> 00:23:30,141
Boss! Where are you?

337
00:23:32,741 --> 00:23:34,900
Ghost! Run!

338
00:23:34,901 --> 00:23:35,941
Run!

339
00:23:36,061 --> 00:23:37,021
So tiny!

340
00:23:37,141 --> 00:23:38,941
Run! Ghost!

341
00:23:39,501 --> 00:23:41,061
Small kid is my master?

342
00:23:42,381 --> 00:23:44,101
Mummy!

343
00:23:45,861 --> 00:23:47,421
Mummy! Save me from this devil!

344
00:23:50,221 --> 00:23:51,101
Gone...

345
00:23:54,461 --> 00:23:55,301
Gone.

346
00:23:57,141 --> 00:23:58,181
Gone.

347
00:24:03,261 --> 00:24:04,421
Where did he go?

348
00:24:06,501 --> 00:24:07,781
Where are you lost?

349
00:24:09,581 --> 00:24:10,901
Your slave is here.

350
00:24:11,341 --> 00:24:13,421
De... De...
Devil!

351
00:24:14,581 --> 00:24:16,341
Save me!

352
00:24:16,621 --> 00:24:19,221
Help!

353
00:24:21,661 --> 00:24:23,661
Devil!
- Tired?

354
00:24:23,821 --> 00:24:25,061
Shall I give you massage?

355
00:24:26,661 --> 00:24:28,021
Devil!

356
00:24:32,861 --> 00:24:34,060
Don't run, boss.

357
00:24:34,061 --> 00:24:35,221
No fun!

358
00:24:35,461 --> 00:24:36,341
You'll fall down.

359
00:24:39,461 --> 00:24:41,581
Smart boy!
- Devil!

360
00:24:42,501 --> 00:24:44,141
Help! Help!

361
00:24:44,381 --> 00:24:45,661
Stop my boss!

362
00:24:56,021 --> 00:24:58,661
This is not a soft sofa,
it is my hand.

363
00:24:59,621 --> 00:25:00,741
I'm telling the truth.

364
00:25:00,901 --> 00:25:02,821
Why are you getting tired
by running?

365
00:25:05,381 --> 00:25:06,381
Oh-oh!

366
00:25:06,701 --> 00:25:07,701
He's down.

367
00:25:09,981 --> 00:25:13,341
I feel as if he got scared
after seeing me.

368
00:25:14,661 --> 00:25:15,821
My boss!

369
00:25:21,901 --> 00:25:23,421
I think the boss is doing yoga.

370
00:25:24,901 --> 00:25:27,021
What shall I do?
What shall I do now?

371
00:25:28,541 --> 00:25:29,421
Hmm.

372
00:25:29,701 --> 00:25:32,661
[Chant]

373
00:25:36,861 --> 00:25:38,141
There is water in stone.

374
00:25:44,621 --> 00:25:45,701
Thank you rock stone.

375
00:25:50,461 --> 00:25:51,381
My boss.

376
00:25:53,381 --> 00:25:54,221
Don't fear.

377
00:26:02,341 --> 00:26:03,821
[Chant]

378
00:26:04,981 --> 00:26:06,781
[Chant]

379
00:26:27,061 --> 00:26:28,741
Run! Run!

380
00:26:29,541 --> 00:26:31,461
Help!

381
00:26:35,741 --> 00:26:38,461
He's frightened of me
like a goat after seeing tiger.

382
00:26:40,101 --> 00:26:43,661
I think I look more like a
band music player than a genie.

383
00:26:44,421 --> 00:26:46,221
I'll make him my friend.

384
00:26:46,661 --> 00:26:48,381
I swear on my genie world.

385
00:26:49,261 --> 00:26:52,101
And then we both friends
will have tea and toast.

386
00:26:55,861 --> 00:26:56,861
Where did you go?

387
00:26:56,981 --> 00:26:59,061
We all became worried
by searching for you.

388
00:26:59,941 --> 00:27:02,301
You'll never mend your ways
even now, go inside.

389
00:27:08,181 --> 00:27:10,100
Are you hungry?
- No, madam.

390
00:27:10,101 --> 00:27:11,141
See there!

391
00:27:11,501 --> 00:27:12,821
Hey slow!

392
00:27:13,981 --> 00:27:16,301
Boss, you were searching
for me, right? - Hmm.

393
00:27:20,581 --> 00:27:22,381
What happened? Why are you shouting?

394
00:27:22,581 --> 00:27:24,141
Look here.

395
00:27:24,621 --> 00:27:26,701
What happened? There is
nobody next to you.

396
00:27:30,581 --> 00:27:33,341
Nobody can see me other than you.

397
00:27:45,381 --> 00:27:46,541
(Sobbing)

398
00:28:22,541 --> 00:28:24,300
This is my younger sister's
wedding card.

399
00:28:24,301 --> 00:28:24,980
Sit down.

400
00:28:24,981 --> 00:28:27,021
Come home one month
before the wedding.

401
00:28:27,261 --> 00:28:28,740
You make all the arrangements.

402
00:28:28,741 --> 00:28:32,541
You go back to your house
after one month of wedding.

403
00:28:32,661 --> 00:28:33,621
Okay, brother.

404
00:28:36,541 --> 00:28:37,980
She was so small,

405
00:28:37,981 --> 00:28:39,660
and now she's getting married.

406
00:28:39,661 --> 00:28:42,781
Girls grow up very fast,
like Vande Bharat.

407
00:28:45,981 --> 00:28:48,340
Look, who has come.

408
00:28:48,341 --> 00:28:50,580
Say hi to uncle.
- Hi dear Thiru.

409
00:28:50,581 --> 00:28:52,941
Didn't recognize the
moustache uncle?

410
00:28:53,381 --> 00:28:54,741
Mummy...

411
00:28:55,381 --> 00:28:56,581
Devil!

412
00:28:58,061 --> 00:28:58,901
Hey!

413
00:28:59,341 --> 00:29:01,461
He's your uncle, talk nicely.

414
00:29:04,021 --> 00:29:06,221
He is not uncle...
he's devil.

415
00:29:06,381 --> 00:29:08,981
Is he saying so
because of my moustache?

416
00:29:11,381 --> 00:29:13,661
Look how he is
twirling his moustache.

417
00:29:14,181 --> 00:29:17,341
No, Thiru. Keep quiet.
Don't say like that.

418
00:29:18,861 --> 00:29:19,740
It is not his mistake.

419
00:29:19,741 --> 00:29:21,621
There are lice
inside the moustache.

420
00:29:21,981 --> 00:29:24,021
Look... devil is laughing.

421
00:29:24,181 --> 00:29:25,181
He's pulling me.

422
00:29:25,621 --> 00:29:29,061
Okay, sister, you come on
the wedding day itself, that's fine.

423
00:29:29,221 --> 00:29:32,141
Brother, eat and go.
- No, no, my stomach is full.

424
00:29:32,621 --> 00:29:35,021
Look, dear. Don't watch
scary cartoons.

425
00:29:35,141 --> 00:29:36,901
Bye!

426
00:29:37,181 --> 00:29:38,301
Don't come again.

427
00:29:38,901 --> 00:29:41,020
I get scared by watching you.

428
00:29:41,021 --> 00:29:43,581
So leave from here.
- Keep quiet.

429
00:29:43,821 --> 00:29:45,781
Sorry, brother, he's just a kid.

430
00:29:46,021 --> 00:29:47,180
Don't feel bad, please.

431
00:29:47,181 --> 00:29:48,981
What to do? My face is scary.
- Bye.

432
00:29:49,101 --> 00:29:51,861
Kids find my moustache to be funny.

433
00:29:51,981 --> 00:29:53,140
I'll shave the moustache.

434
00:29:53,141 --> 00:29:55,301
Look, devil is escaping.
- Thiru!

435
00:29:55,501 --> 00:29:56,461
Shut your mouth!

436
00:30:06,661 --> 00:30:09,101
My boss, is everything fine?

437
00:30:11,261 --> 00:30:12,341
Shall I remove shoes?

438
00:30:13,781 --> 00:30:14,701
It's me.

439
00:30:15,181 --> 00:30:16,021
Mamma!

440
00:30:17,141 --> 00:30:18,261
What happened, son?

441
00:30:18,741 --> 00:30:20,461
Mother, de... de...

442
00:30:20,661 --> 00:30:22,021
Feeling hungry?

443
00:30:22,301 --> 00:30:23,221
No, mother.

444
00:30:23,581 --> 00:30:26,661
De... de... -Laddoos?
Okay, I'll bring right now.

445
00:30:31,781 --> 00:30:33,541
By the way, who are you?

446
00:30:33,941 --> 00:30:35,421
Why are you following me?

447
00:30:35,541 --> 00:30:38,061
I feel scared
by seeing you. - Oh!

448
00:30:38,701 --> 00:30:40,981
That's why I don't see
myself in the mirror.

449
00:30:44,421 --> 00:30:46,261
What if I change my get up?

450
00:30:48,941 --> 00:30:50,021
How do I look?

451
00:31:01,381 --> 00:31:02,301
Fatty!

452
00:31:02,901 --> 00:31:03,941
How am I?

453
00:31:07,181 --> 00:31:08,301
Thin!

454
00:31:12,941 --> 00:31:14,061
How is it now?

455
00:31:15,461 --> 00:31:19,821
I love you. (Bengali)

456
00:31:20,501 --> 00:31:22,780
I love you.

457
00:31:22,781 --> 00:31:23,700
I...

458
00:31:23,701 --> 00:31:24,621
How is it now?

459
00:31:24,741 --> 00:31:26,541
Ninja!

460
00:31:27,261 --> 00:31:29,701
Yay!

461
00:31:31,021 --> 00:31:31,901
Yay!

462
00:31:32,581 --> 00:31:37,541
(Boy laughing)

463
00:31:38,501 --> 00:31:39,781
How is it now?

464
00:31:40,101 --> 00:31:41,101
Bhim!

465
00:31:44,101 --> 00:31:45,701
Bhim! Bhim! Bhim!

466
00:31:46,421 --> 00:31:48,501
Chhota Bhim!
Chhota Bhim!

467
00:31:54,181 --> 00:31:55,260
How is it now?

468
00:31:55,261 --> 00:31:56,901
Uniform like mine.

469
00:31:59,221 --> 00:32:01,181
Who are you?

470
00:32:01,461 --> 00:32:02,821
Do you work in circus?

471
00:32:02,941 --> 00:32:06,581
I'm Karkimuki, king of Genie world.

472
00:32:07,821 --> 00:32:11,661
3000 years back a sage has cured me
and turned me into a statue.

473
00:32:11,901 --> 00:32:13,341
And you freed me.

474
00:32:13,701 --> 00:32:15,821
That's why I'm here to serve you.

475
00:32:16,101 --> 00:32:17,701
I'll do whatever you say.

476
00:32:19,181 --> 00:32:20,940
You're speaking pure Hindi.

477
00:32:20,941 --> 00:32:22,621
I didn't understand anything.

478
00:32:22,941 --> 00:32:24,421
Talk Mumbai Hindi.

479
00:32:25,101 --> 00:32:26,781
Mumbai Hindi...

480
00:32:26,981 --> 00:32:29,981
Mix of Urdu, Hindi,
Marathi and Punjabi.

481
00:32:39,581 --> 00:32:40,941
Actually the thing is,

482
00:32:41,141 --> 00:32:44,021
3000 years back a sage has
cursed me.

483
00:32:44,341 --> 00:32:46,101
And you made me free of it.

484
00:32:46,381 --> 00:32:47,901
So I came to repay the favour.

485
00:32:48,981 --> 00:32:50,021
I'm your friend...

486
00:32:50,261 --> 00:32:51,381
I mean bestie.

487
00:32:52,421 --> 00:32:53,381
Yes!

488
00:32:56,061 --> 00:32:56,901
Yes?

489
00:33:44,181 --> 00:33:46,021
Why did you.... hit him?

490
00:33:46,181 --> 00:33:48,020
Whoever troubles my boss,

491
00:33:48,021 --> 00:33:50,661
I'll burn him into ashes.

492
00:33:51,381 --> 00:33:53,381
I mean he will be dead.

493
00:33:54,821 --> 00:33:56,101
Do you understand?

494
00:34:02,301 --> 00:34:05,181
3 Idiots! I'm coming!

495
00:34:05,621 --> 00:34:06,581
I'm too coming!

496
00:34:07,341 --> 00:34:08,220
My boss!

497
00:34:08,221 --> 00:34:10,901
Give the ball to me!
- Give me! - Pass it!

498
00:34:39,581 --> 00:34:42,381
Why is he walking like that?
Injured his leg?

499
00:34:42,781 --> 00:34:45,421
We'll break him leg too now.

500
00:35:03,541 --> 00:35:04,661
What are you watching?

501
00:35:04,821 --> 00:35:07,501
You all have....troubled me a lot.

502
00:35:08,141 --> 00:35:09,821
Sorry to me.

503
00:35:10,221 --> 00:35:11,701
I'll not say.
What will you do?

504
00:35:12,341 --> 00:35:14,381
It'll be bad...
if you don't say.

505
00:35:15,261 --> 00:35:17,141
Stop your overacting.

506
00:35:17,981 --> 00:35:19,621
Leave quietly from here. Okay.

507
00:35:21,101 --> 00:35:23,220
Are you... saying sorry or not?

508
00:35:23,221 --> 00:35:25,461
Stammering boy!
I'll not say, leave!

509
00:35:28,981 --> 00:35:30,500
I'll let you play if you say sorry.

510
00:35:30,501 --> 00:35:32,861
Hey, take the ball from him.

511
00:35:50,661 --> 00:35:52,181
Hey, pull it.

512
00:36:06,181 --> 00:36:07,461
Come on!

513
00:36:15,461 --> 00:36:16,741
I'll catch it now.

514
00:36:17,341 --> 00:36:19,820
What are you doing?
Catch it. - Catch it if you can.

515
00:36:19,821 --> 00:36:21,700
Hey!

516
00:36:21,701 --> 00:36:23,261
You troubled me a lot, right?

517
00:36:23,901 --> 00:36:26,940
Thiru will take revenge
for everything.

518
00:36:26,941 --> 00:36:28,301
Run! Run!

519
00:36:28,901 --> 00:36:30,101
Come on, catch.

520
00:36:33,381 --> 00:36:34,581
I'm tired!

521
00:36:44,421 --> 00:36:45,341
Got it!

522
00:36:45,461 --> 00:36:46,940
Move I say!

523
00:36:46,941 --> 00:36:48,421
I'll get crushed.

524
00:36:52,661 --> 00:36:53,821
Hey!

525
00:36:54,261 --> 00:36:55,661
Why is the hall flying?

526
00:36:56,101 --> 00:36:58,381
I'll fall down!

527
00:37:00,701 --> 00:37:02,781
Are you hurt?
- Come, come.

528
00:37:06,621 --> 00:37:07,861
At your service.

529
00:37:09,981 --> 00:37:11,061
It's paining.

530
00:37:13,621 --> 00:37:15,981
What do you say?
I got it, right?

531
00:37:16,701 --> 00:37:17,340
Ouch!

532
00:37:17,341 --> 00:37:19,021
His shorts came down.

533
00:37:19,461 --> 00:37:21,341
Yours too!

534
00:37:21,941 --> 00:37:23,261
Mine too!

535
00:37:23,861 --> 00:37:25,140
Run! Run!

536
00:37:25,141 --> 00:37:26,941
Save yourself by running away!

537
00:37:34,101 --> 00:37:35,621
No water.

538
00:37:35,901 --> 00:37:37,701
What happened?
- Shower isn't working.

539
00:37:38,501 --> 00:37:40,741
Wow! See the water.

540
00:37:46,901 --> 00:37:47,741
Oh!

541
00:37:49,341 --> 00:37:50,221
No!

542
00:37:57,181 --> 00:37:59,061
Will you eat egg?
No? I'll eat.

543
