with empty stomach.

1352
01:31:21,421 --> 01:31:23,461
Listen to my words. Eat.

1353
01:31:27,261 --> 01:31:28,101
Thiru.

1354
01:31:29,061 --> 01:31:33,421
Whatever mom does,
she will do only for your good.

1355
01:31:35,941 --> 01:31:37,021
Eat a little, dear.

1356
01:31:40,901 --> 01:31:42,701
Hey, are you really a doctor?

1357
01:31:43,021 --> 01:31:45,140
I brought my daughter
for treatment believing you, right?

1358
01:31:45,141 --> 01:31:46,180
Don't get angry.

1359
01:31:46,181 --> 01:31:47,260
Talk a little patiently.

1360
01:31:47,261 --> 01:31:48,581
I want to kill you.

1361
01:31:48,701 --> 01:31:50,661
You made his life hell.

1362
01:31:51,501 --> 01:31:53,660
Though she stammered,
my daughter used to talk well.

1363
01:31:53,661 --> 01:31:56,901
After operation, she's mute.
Are you a doctor?

1364
01:31:57,061 --> 01:31:58,500
Listen, I will...

1365
01:31:58,501 --> 01:31:59,941
How can I talk calmly, man?

1366
01:32:00,941 --> 01:32:01,901
Here.

1367
01:32:03,021 --> 01:32:04,420
Whatever happened has happened.

1368
01:32:04,421 --> 01:32:07,141
I have given five lakhs
more than what you spent.

1369
01:32:07,461 --> 01:32:08,580
Leave this matter here

1370
01:32:08,581 --> 01:32:10,181
without making it big, please.

1371
01:32:10,581 --> 01:32:11,501
Please!

1372
01:33:33,301 --> 01:33:34,581
Sir. It's him, sir.

1373
01:33:34,781 --> 01:33:35,661
Arrest him.

1374
01:33:42,661 --> 01:33:43,941
Madam! Who are you, madam?

1375
01:33:44,421 --> 01:33:45,741
He is my son, sir.

1376
01:33:45,941 --> 01:33:47,461
You seem to look educated.

1377
01:33:47,581 --> 01:33:49,341
Won't you enquire about the doctor

1378
01:33:49,461 --> 01:33:52,260
who does the treatment and
the genuineness of the hospital?

1379
01:33:52,261 --> 01:33:55,341
If we had been a little late, your
son's would lose his life.

1380
01:34:00,501 --> 01:34:01,860
I made a big mistake, Deepa.

1381
01:34:01,861 --> 01:34:03,261
Stop overthinking.

1382
01:34:03,381 --> 01:34:04,660
Stop worrying.
All is well!

1383
01:34:04,661 --> 01:34:07,060
I did this so that Thiru talks well.

1384
01:34:07,061 --> 01:34:09,581
But now I don't understand
what to do.

1385
01:34:09,821 --> 01:34:11,781
I know a doctor.
Go to him.

1386
01:34:12,061 --> 01:34:12,981
Okay.

1387
01:34:15,781 --> 01:34:16,861
First of all,

1388
01:34:16,981 --> 01:34:19,941
for those
who have this stammering problem,

1389
01:34:20,061 --> 01:34:22,860
it is impossible to cure them
with medicine or operation.

1390
01:34:22,861 --> 01:34:25,500
You may go abroad
for the treatment.

1391
01:34:25,501 --> 01:34:28,301
It is a total waste to spend money
and time for this.

1392
01:34:28,661 --> 01:34:31,140
To treat this illness,

1393
01:34:31,141 --> 01:34:33,381
you need to get rid of his fear.

1394
01:34:34,741 --> 01:34:37,821
What we need to do
is first allow him to talk.

1395
01:34:37,941 --> 01:34:40,781
Stop making his feel
he's has a flaw?

1396
01:34:42,381 --> 01:34:44,661
When we are not
paying attention to them,

1397
01:34:44,781 --> 01:34:48,501
it affects them immensely.

1398
01:34:48,661 --> 01:34:50,981
So, we need to pay attention.

1399
01:34:52,341 --> 01:34:54,020
If you ensure him

1400
01:34:54,021 --> 01:34:56,901
whatever he says is right,
it will build his confidence.

1401
01:34:58,061 --> 01:35:01,181
You can do his treatment
for that a doctor is not needed.

1402
01:35:15,901 --> 01:35:17,221
'Today is the 48th day.'

1403
01:35:20,501 --> 01:35:22,141
'This is my last day.'

1404
01:35:35,781 --> 01:35:36,941
Sorry dear.

1405
01:35:39,301 --> 01:35:42,061
Hereafter, whatever you
want to talk, talk to me boldly.

1406
01:35:42,581 --> 01:35:44,021
I will listen to it. Okay?

1407
01:35:44,541 --> 01:35:45,701
Say something.

1408
01:35:50,461 --> 01:35:51,541
No, mom.

1409
01:35:53,461 --> 01:35:55,661
You won't listen.

1410
01:35:56,101 --> 01:35:57,101
Thiru!

1411
01:35:57,581 --> 01:36:00,301
whatever your mom does,
she will do for your good, dear.

1412
01:36:01,901 --> 01:36:06,661
You didn't want others
to mock at me,

1413
01:36:07,221 --> 01:36:09,261
but when did you listen to my words?

1414
01:36:12,141 --> 01:36:15,461
Whenever I talk,
you give 10 options.

1415
01:36:17,101 --> 01:36:19,700
'There is bread, there is papaya,
there is banana, there is biscuit.'

1416
01:36:19,701 --> 01:36:20,700
And almond milk.

1417
01:36:20,701 --> 01:36:22,661
'Tell me. What do you want?'

1418
01:36:25,061 --> 01:36:28,581
But Shendi allowed me to talk.

1419
01:36:29,141 --> 01:36:32,661
and listened patiently
and completely to whatever I spoke.

1420
01:36:38,821 --> 01:36:43,381
I lost in a competition just once,

1421
01:36:43,541 --> 01:36:48,101
as you always broke my confidence.

1422
01:36:48,381 --> 01:36:52,660
But Shendi

1423
01:36:52,661 --> 01:36:54,541
encouraged me always.

1424
01:36:54,941 --> 01:36:57,141
That's why, I won.

1425
01:37:02,821 --> 01:37:08,101
Only because of that confidence,
I won where I lost, mom.

1426
01:37:08,421 --> 01:37:11,781
I won for the first time in my life, mom.

1427
01:37:15,941 --> 01:37:17,461
Those who made fun of me,

1428
01:37:17,581 --> 01:37:18,980
it made them my friends.

1429
01:37:18,981 --> 01:37:21,581
It brought me good name
from the teachers.

1430
01:37:21,901 --> 01:37:25,381
It did a lot more good things
for me, mom.

1431
01:37:25,541 --> 01:37:29,381
On that day, Jini saved you
from those thieves, mom.

1432
01:37:36,061 --> 01:37:39,341
You never took me seriously.

1433
01:37:39,461 --> 01:37:41,901
I never suffered

1434
01:37:42,421 --> 01:37:44,821
till that ghost was with me, mom.

1435
01:37:55,621 --> 01:37:57,741
He took care of me.

1436
01:37:57,901 --> 01:38:00,221
Loved me.

1437
01:38:00,381 --> 01:38:03,021
You separated me from it, mom.

1438
01:38:14,661 --> 01:38:16,421
I won't talk to you.

1439
01:38:18,901 --> 01:38:19,821
Thiru,

1440
01:38:20,141 --> 01:38:22,141
Hey... hey wait!

1441
01:38:29,021 --> 01:38:30,541
Thiru, wait!

1442
01:38:31,381 --> 01:38:33,661
Thiru! Wait!

1443
01:38:34,701 --> 01:38:36,381
Shendi! Shendi!

1444
01:38:37,861 --> 01:38:39,101
Shendi!

1445
01:38:44,541 --> 01:38:45,461
Shendi!

1446
01:38:49,901 --> 01:38:51,381
Go home.

1447
01:38:53,101 --> 01:38:54,261
I will read the mantra.

1448
01:38:54,621 --> 01:38:56,181
I will read it.

1449
01:38:57,701 --> 01:38:58,821
I will read it.

1450
01:38:59,581 --> 01:39:00,621
(chant)

1451
01:39:03,541 --> 01:39:05,541
(chant)

1452
01:39:06,501 --> 01:39:08,421
(chant)

1453
01:39:10,221 --> 01:39:12,821
(chant)

1454
01:39:16,741 --> 01:39:17,581
(chant)

1455
01:39:19,821 --> 01:39:22,381
No!

1456
01:39:22,661 --> 01:39:23,541
(chant)

1457
01:39:31,941 --> 01:39:33,781
(chant)

1458
01:39:42,981 --> 01:39:44,781
(chant)

1459
01:39:45,821 --> 01:39:48,861
(chant)

1460
01:39:51,181 --> 01:39:54,501
(chant)

1461
01:39:54,861 --> 01:39:55,741
(chant)

1462
01:39:56,421 --> 01:39:59,141
(chant)

1463
01:40:00,101 --> 01:40:03,461
(chant)

1464
01:40:03,901 --> 01:40:06,141
(chant)

1465
01:40:06,701 --> 01:40:09,061
(chant)

1466
01:40:11,101 --> 01:40:11,981
Thiru!

1467
01:40:13,981 --> 01:40:16,301
Thiru, you stopped stammering.

1468
01:40:49,621 --> 01:40:50,621
Master.

1469
01:40:54,861 --> 01:40:55,701
Hey!

1470
01:41:05,661 --> 01:41:06,701
Master.

1471
01:41:09,181 --> 01:41:10,541
Shendi!

1472
01:41:11,021 --> 01:41:12,421
Shendi!

1473
01:41:15,021 --> 01:41:16,341
Shendi!

1474
01:41:31,141 --> 01:41:32,021
Hey!

1475
01:41:42,461 --> 01:41:43,421
Mom!

1476
01:41:43,781 --> 01:41:45,581
Mom!

1477
01:41:46,141 --> 01:41:47,301
Get up, mom.

1478
01:41:47,621 --> 01:41:48,741
Get up, mom.

1479
01:41:49,261 --> 01:41:50,901
Mom, what is wrong?

1480
01:41:51,221 --> 01:41:52,941
Get up, mom.

1481
01:41:53,261 --> 01:41:55,061
Get up, mom.

1482
01:41:55,341 --> 01:41:57,021
Mom...

1483
01:41:57,381 --> 01:41:58,541
Mom...

1484
01:42:01,301 --> 01:42:02,701
Mom...

1485
01:42:03,861 --> 01:42:05,261
Mom...

1486
01:42:05,621 --> 01:42:06,901
Mom...

1487
01:42:07,581 --> 01:42:09,821
Mom. Get up, mom.

1488
01:42:10,181 --> 01:42:12,061
Mom, what is it?

1489
01:42:13,581 --> 01:42:14,741
Mom...

1490
01:42:15,261 --> 01:42:17,261
Mom...

1491
01:42:20,821 --> 01:42:23,181
Get up, mom.

1492
01:42:24,501 --> 01:42:25,461
Mom...

1493
01:42:25,901 --> 01:42:27,661
'Ghosts have certain rules.'

1494
01:42:28,301 --> 01:42:30,541
'We should not bring
back dead people alive,'

1495
01:42:31,421 --> 01:42:33,061
