1496
01:42:33,701 --> 01:42:36,221
'solve problems that
are related to the heart.'

1497
01:42:37,021 --> 01:42:38,661
'If we go against these rules,'

1498
01:42:39,141 --> 01:42:43,141
'we will be punished for
Brahma dosha and I will die.'

1499
01:42:54,221 --> 01:42:55,861
Mom.

1500
01:43:00,301 --> 01:43:01,741
Mom.

1501
01:43:09,221 --> 01:43:11,500
Please get up!

1502
01:43:11,501 --> 01:43:13,101
Mom! Mom!

1503
01:43:13,581 --> 01:43:15,381
Please get up!

1504
01:43:15,541 --> 01:43:16,781
Get up!

1505
01:43:28,821 --> 01:43:29,661
Mom...

1506
01:43:34,821 --> 01:43:35,661
Thiru!

1507
01:43:36,101 --> 01:43:37,301
Mom...

1508
01:43:37,781 --> 01:43:38,741
Mom...

1509
01:43:39,581 --> 01:43:40,621
Mom...

1510
01:43:57,261 --> 01:44:01,101
Thiru, I cannot see you sad.

1511
01:44:02,021 --> 01:44:03,701
I want to see you happy.

1512
01:44:28,461 --> 01:44:29,461
Shendi!

1513
01:44:31,461 --> 01:44:32,621
Shendi!

1514
01:44:34,541 --> 01:44:35,661
Shendi!

1515
01:44:37,581 --> 01:44:38,621
Shendi!

1516
01:44:40,461 --> 01:44:41,461
Thiru!

1517
01:44:45,741 --> 01:44:47,501
The young poet of this state

1518
01:44:47,661 --> 01:44:49,741
wants to present you some poems.

1519
01:44:49,981 --> 01:44:51,541
Please listen to him carefully.

1520
01:44:53,661 --> 01:44:55,260
Hope. Hopelessness. Desire.

1521
01:44:55,261 --> 01:44:57,100
Language. Drama. Passion.

1522
01:44:57,101 --> 01:44:59,501
Apiration. Intoxication. Origin.

1523
01:44:59,621 --> 01:45:01,460
Sweet. A wave. Wisdom.

1524
01:45:01,461 --> 01:45:03,740
Brilliant. Radiant. Beautiful!

1525
01:45:03,741 --> 01:45:06,181
Kavita. Babita. Sarita.

1526
01:45:06,301 --> 01:45:08,540
Shakila. Jamela. Pathela.

1527
01:45:08,541 --> 01:45:11,021
Rihana. Sultana. Ruksana.

1528
01:45:11,141 --> 01:45:13,260
Julie. Tulip. Mona. Sona.

1529
01:45:13,261 --> 01:45:14,941
Food. Eat. Drink.

1530
01:45:15,061 --> 01:45:16,980
Sit. Get up. Lie down.

1531
01:45:16,981 --> 01:45:18,540
Reena. Tina.

1532
01:45:18,541 --> 01:45:19,861
Sweat. Bath.

1533
01:45:19,981 --> 01:45:21,060
Wash. Cry.

1534
01:45:21,061 --> 01:45:22,420
Youth. Mosquito net.

1535
01:45:22,421 --> 01:45:23,861
Story. Grandma.

1536
01:45:23,981 --> 01:45:25,741
One rupee. Two rupees.

1537
01:45:25,861 --> 01:45:27,900
Four rupees. Come forward
and go behind.

1538
01:45:27,901 --> 01:45:29,660
Come if you wish or don't.

1539
01:45:29,661 --> 01:45:31,420
Eat. Treasure. Banana.

1540
01:45:31,421 --> 01:45:33,220
Rizwana. Farzana. Come tomorrow.

1541
01:45:33,221 --> 01:45:34,980
Lovely. Adorable. Fascinating.

1542
01:45:34,981 --> 01:45:37,941
Fish. Lizard. Brocolli. Peanuts.

1543
01:45:38,061 --> 01:45:40,941
Road. Path. Way. Swing.

1544
01:45:41,061 --> 01:45:42,261
Did you hear

1545
01:45:42,381 --> 01:45:44,340
neither from East nor from West.

1546
01:45:44,341 --> 01:45:46,341
Nor from North or from South.

1547
01:45:46,501 --> 01:45:49,221
I spoke it through my mouth.
